\f2\b \cf0 \strokec2 They are the same equation.
\f0\b0  The structure is isomorphic. \uc0\u954  plays the role of the hazard rate. \u953  plays the role of the risk-free discount rate. The stopping time \u952  in the perpetual framework 
\f1\i is
