This isn't a metaphor or an analogy. It is a 
\f2\b formal mathematical equivalence
\f0\b0 . The Ackerer framework, developed for crypto futures pricing, accidentally \'97 or perhaps inevitably \'97 rediscovered the entire mathematical architecture of credit risk pricing.\
