\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The Duffie-Singleton framework and its descendants \'97 which currently price trillions of dollars of credit default swaps, corporate bonds, sukuk, and insurance products \'97 require:\
